event.title: Beauty Times
event.description:
Beauty Times Various types of beauty products for the lips

Nowadays, cosmetics that are applied to the lips are increasingly diverse. Starting from lip moisturizing lip balm used before lipstick, to lip gloss using lipstick to display a sexy glossy feel.

www.beautimes.co For lip color, you are certainly familiar with lipstick. Currently there are also lipsticks offered in various types such as matte, glossy, and butter.

Every face you makeup and the model of makeup you do requires different lip color. So, you must be prepared to have various types and shades of this lip color.
